entries.femaleVariant: Discharged booster.
Either of you use energy boosters?
I don't, and not that I know of. Jeff, maybe? He works so hard…
Bullet holes – caulked up…
Someone tried to patch up the bullet holes. Assuming neither of you had anything to do with this?
Bloodstains... Not quite scrubbed clean.
Where's the blood from? It yours?
I'm one hundred percent sure it's not ours. Maybe the intruder's?
Why's this door concealed?
Where? There's no door here.
Right here. It's closed.
Department of Law at Asukaga-Berkeley? Hm, classy…
You and Jeff graduate from the same school? Must've been expensive…
We were lucky. On full scholarships, funded by the Night Foundation.
Broken?
It was fine a couple days ago. We rarely use it, though.
Wedding pic? Interesting backdrop…
Blue roses. You sure? Roses in this picture look pretty red to me.
entries.maleVariant: Heh, blue roses. Wha-you sure? 'Cause the roses in this picture look pretty red to me.

entries.femaleVariant: Odd... tech's practically prehistoric, but it doesn't look older than a day…
Saw somethin' like this back in the war. Transmitters – Militech was using 'em.
Got a vizh on our receiver – black van parked next to it. Gotta be our winner.
entries.maleVariant: Got a vizh on the receiver – black van parked next to it. Gotta be our winner.

entries.femaleVariant: Tight bites? You and Jeff must be puttin' in serious overtime.
entries.maleVariant: Heh, tight bites? You and Jeff must be puttin' in serious overtime.

entries.femaleVariant: Elections. You don't even have time to think about food, so you just order whatever's quickest.
Weird hardware... What's it for?
Used meds. Intruder make a beeline here after Jeff tagged him?
Fresh fruit... tasty, by the looks of it.
They deliver it to us –  it's included in the rent.
What was that?
No fuckin' clue. Felt kinda good, but weird. Like tripping on acid.
That happen to the screen a lot? Or to any of the others?
entries.maleVariant: Does that happen to the screen a lot? Or to any of the others?

entries.femaleVariant: Wonder how long they've been keepin' this from you.
entries.maleVariant: Wonder how long they been keepin' this from you.

entries.femaleVariant: Jesus Christ…
Looks like it's been enhanced. What have we got here…?
entries.maleVariant: Looks like it's been enhanced. What've we got here…?

entries.femaleVariant: There's some weird chem stuff in here... Enhanced food?
It's "SmartFood." It's enhanced for improved mental performance.
Fresh Fruit for Rotting Vegetables...
Scanner's showin' somethin' different.
Wait... you mean here?
Line-of-sight? Let's look around, see if we can't spot where our receiver's camping out…
Connected to the wall-mounted screens. Wonder where else these cables run…
But yes, it's true Jeff hasn't eaten anything else recently...
Glutamine, noradrenaline, dopamine, serotonin... all neurotransmitters. Know anything about this?
I don't know if it really works, but people believe it. Other than that... it isn't half bad.
What? It was a sick album.
But it wouldn't be like him. He's always been against using any... substances.
No, of course not.
No. Open it…  somehow, please.
A charity founded by Richard Night's widow.
They helped a lot of underprivileged kids with ambitions.
Any? Nicotine's a substance.
Jefferson has never smoked.
Really? Could've sworn I've seen him smoking…
entries.maleVariant: Really? Could've sworn I've seen him smokin'…

entries.femaleVariant: Jeff? No, never. He doesn't go near the stuff.
I wanted blue roses. So we ordered a whole truckload.
Hmm... of course, you're right. They didn't have blue roses, I forgot…
I don't understand...
What just happened a second ago. Didn't see it?
entries.maleVariant: What just happened a second ago. You didn't see it?

entries.femaleVariant: No... what?
Uh, never mind.
Too long. This ends now. I'm not letting any more of those freaks set foot--
Iron... This Jeff's?
Mh. Mine, actually. But yes, that's the one Jeff used that night.
[Fix screen]
Probably.
Previous owners, left over, maybe?
Think we're safe puttin' your security at the top of our list of suspects.
They violated our privacy... The sons of bitches! Under my own roof!
Don't worry about me. Do what you have to do.
Someone's been pullin' all-nighters.
Talkin' to yourself again?
More and more – ever since this terrorist started stalking me…
Short range UHF. Signal only travels line-of-sight, but it can't be intercepted.
Wonder how long they've been hiding this from you.
Never noticed anything, had any reason to suspect?
Ever noticed anything out of the ordinary, suspicious?
That they're violating our trust, watching our every move?
That they'd concealed a goddamn secret room full of spy stuff in our own apartment?
So you didn't notice – OK.
Ugh... my head...
Something wrong?
The hell is this all for, though...?
entries.maleVariant: The hell is all this for, though...?

entries.femaleVariant: Fuck if I know. But my gut tells me we should see what this bad boy's hooked up to. See these cables?
You and Jefferson – you've come a long way.
To get from Heywood all the way here... it's no easy thing.
Yes. If you aren't born with a silver shard, your chances are slim.
And if you're born in Heywood, they're almost nonexistent...
It looks like SSI's employees knew about the break-in.
Maybe it's worth checking their office downstairs...
This is Jeff's personal machine. I doubt you'll find anything on it relating to the break-in.
Is this Jeff's gun?
Law department  at Asukaga... Not bad.
Wedding photo?
TV's broken?
Right here.
Bloodstains...?
Bloodstains...?
Bloodstains...?
Bloodstains...?
Bloodstains...?
Caulked-up bullet holes?
Tech's prehistoric, but it looks new...
Wonder what this is for.
Fresh fruit... must be tasty.
Used meds?
Tight bites?
Tight bites? Really?
Cheap grub?
Discharged booster?
I find this so hard to believe…
How could they do this to us? The gall…
Seems a happy fam. That your daughter?
Xochi… oh, we miss her. Her studies took her abroad.
Huh, where to?
Europe. An excellent school, she'll get a good education…
I know, it's an ocean away… But with Jeff running for mayor… it's just safer this way.
Cables lead here... Gotta be another way inside. Sharp eye, Johnny!
That your daughter?
